snippet: Actress Misty Upham, who played a housekeeper in the movie adaption of "August: Osage County," has been missing in Washington state for six days, police said on Friday....

headline.print_headline: Actress Misty Upham Reported Missing in Washington State: Police
headline.main: Actress Misty Upham Reported Missing in Washington State: Police

lead_paragraph: Actress Misty Upham, who played a housekeeper in the movie adaption of "August: Osage County," has been missing in Washington state for six days, police said on Friday.
